<title>Tivoli | Tivoli Kindergarten | Tsing Yi | Hong Kong</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Tivoli nursery and kindergarten campuses nestled in the heart of Tsing Yi cater to learners aged 2-6years old. We offer a trilingual learning for our pre-nursery and K1-3 levels."/>
