農曆年假後的首個工作日，學校特意邀請香港紅十字會的專業團隊為全體員工進行防疫講座、實地視察，進一步加強團隊的防疫能力！💪🏼

下一步就係要召募學生及家長義工擔任「健康大使」。祝大家蛇年進步、平安大吉、身體健康！❤🌷🙏🏼

Children’s safety and health have always been our top priority. To ensure the physical and mental well-being of children, we must all work together on preventive measures! 🤝🏼

On the first working day after the Lunar New Year break, the school specially invited a professional team from the Hong Kong Red Cross to conduct a seminar and on-site inspection for all staff, further strengthening the team‘s preventive strategies! 💪🏼

The next step is to recruit student and parent volunteers to act as ”Health Ambassadors.“ Wishing everyone progress, safety, and good health in the Year of the Snake! ❤🌷🙏🏼" role="button"></div><div><div data-hook="item-wrapper" class="gallery-item-wrapper visible cube-type-fit [object Object]" id="item-wrapper-4a2549f3-25d6-42b3-9535-4b88acc9263a_13" style="background-color:inherit;height:500px;width:500px;margin:0px"><div class="gallery-item-content item-content-regular image-item gallery-item-visible gallery-item gallery-item-preloaded grid-fit  " data-hook="image-item" style="width:500px;height:500px;margin-top:0;margin-left:0"><picture><img src="https://scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.75761-15/476401515_18029733770630559_1862883722225435149_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=108&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=18de74&amp;efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=bKPKRH-_0tkQ7kNvwHaiuce&amp;_nc_oc=AdryG-c8LNoXn5iCVN6wh5fhc8IBujESZ64LG_O0Datj9akEMWBG8kUIbJJeVk-ElU0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&amp;_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&amp;_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQGAF8MnVN7asua4DO5o6eAPOwuo6RO5kI9ebGoH9sB-aYJShZvKRb-LN2XPjUht1LcobGd9sK6d&amp;oh=00_AfzHb8LgMIVpfJpAYTMo6qvMifkeNYPdsXZ5sTyxmvuHlw&amp;oe=69CACE0D" alt="兒童安全及健康一直是我們最關注的重點工作。為兒童身心健康，就要大家一齊做好防疫工作！🤝🏼

