K1嘅小朋友上星期喺學校🏫探索完課室嘅顏色🎨，趁住今日天朗氣清☀️，我哋再一齊出去附近嘅公園🌳，探索大自然嘅顏色🌸🪨🍃🍂

Discovering the Colors of Nature 
Last week, the K1 kids looked at the colors in their classroom 🏫. With today’s beautiful and sunny weather ☀️, we’re heading out to a nearby park 🌳 to explore the colors of nature together 🌸🪨🍃🍂." role="button"></div><div><div data-hook="item-wrapper" class="gallery-item-wrapper visible cube-type-fit [object Object]" id="item-wrapper-4271eca1-776c-411f-8441-0e5383393128_24" style="background-color:inherit;height:500px;width:500px;margin:0px"><div class="gallery-item-content item-content-regular image-item gallery-item-visible gallery-item gallery-item-preloaded grid-fit  " data-hook="image-item" style="width:500px;height:500px;margin-top:0;margin-left:0"><picture><img src="https://scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t39.30808-6/469355095_18022409642630559_7848726595971688533_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=110&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=18de74&amp;efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=xIroVVet9f4Q7kNvwGIM_jp&amp;_nc_oc=Adq9oMq2rme4OTKvIvB69DdrCC5toeXNKUU8BolNiHc6SJYFGETcbappLyzjvtm46Ec&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&amp;_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&amp;_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQEkFLF1pCtIQBfTjhl9D0861kjHjdGJoXyQNBYUTFVOKbHUYG7bIBQ52152Pdrb4IWtHMb9_f65&amp;oh=00_Afz-RFGYT8ckibEGq5vKHj96LkTc0Ynnf-qOPHBbCPpx6A&amp;oe=69CAC7E6" alt="探索大自然的顏色
K1嘅小朋友上星期喺學校🏫探索完課室嘅顏色🎨，趁住今日天朗氣清☀️，我哋再一齊出去附近嘅公園🌳，探索大自然嘅顏色🌸🪨🍃🍂

Discovering the Colors of Nature 
