當日有幾場限定活動，包括：
🎨七感探索之旅
💃🏻創意綜合式幼兒肢體音樂體驗活動
📚英語/普通話/廣東話故事劇場

每個活動都設有名額，唔想錯過嘅就快啲嚟報名喇！

🔗登記參加開放日限定活動：
https://forms.gle/e9erN31CvVa6jVv76

📣Tivoli Kindergarten (Ching Fu) and Tivoli Nursery (Ching Fu) will be hosting open house on August 24, 2024📣

There will be several exclusive activities that day, including:
🎨 Tivoli&#x27;s Multisensory Exploration Journey
💃🏻 Creative Integrated Early Childhood Music and Movement Experience 
📚 Tivoli&#x27;s Storytime Theater

