https://forms.gle/e9erN31CvVa6jVv76" class="gallery-item-visible gallery-item gallery-item-preloaded" style="width:100%;height:100%" data-hook="gallery-item-image-img" loading="lazy"/></picture></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-hook="group-view" class="group-view group-view-32" style="--group-top:0px;--group-left:17600px;--group-width:550px;--group-right:auto" aria-hidden="false"><div data-id="be47fa4c-0fdb-4649-8c80-3e1166ab52e5_32" class="item-link-wrapper" data-idx="32" data-hook="item-link-wrapper" tabindex="-1"><div class="gallery-item-container item-container-regular has-custom-focus visible clickable" id="pgibe47fa4c0fdb46498c803e1166ab52e5_32_32" data-hash="be47fa4c-0fdb-4649-8c80-3e1166ab52e5_32" data-id="be47fa4c-0fdb-4649-8c80-3e1166ab52e5_32" data-idx="32" data-hook="item-container" style="overflow-y:hidden;position:absolute;bottom:auto;margin:25px;top:0;left:17600px;right:auto;width:500px;height:500px;overflow:hidden;transition:opacity .2s ease;opacity:0;display:none"><div data-idx="32" id="item-action-be47fa4c-0fdb-4649-8c80-3e1166ab52e5_32" class="item-action" tabindex="-1" data-hook="item-action" aria-label="🌏 「讓一個想法、或行動變成習慣，需要21天的時間。」—行為心理學家卡爾 雷須利(Karl Lashley)

連續21天，在日常生活中做一點微小改變。也許你會開始習慣，慢慢培養出對地球更好的生活方式。

邀請你一起參加「永續飲食21天」挑戰，每日一餐多菜少肉，一起做到低碳排放。

參加方法：
1. 每天在Instagram / Facebook post一張你的永續飲食相片(Stoty或Post都可以)
2. Tag一位朋友，邀請他/她一同接受挑戰
3. Hashtag #tivoli21dayschallenge 

獎項：
本校學生：成功完成21天挑戰者，將於本年度成果分享會暨畢業典禮中頒發獎狀，以作鼓勵！
公眾人士：成功完成21天挑戰者，將會邀請出席本年度成果分享會暨畢業典禮，並會頒發獎狀，以作鼓勵！

🌏 It takes 21 days for an idea or action to become a habit.” - Behavioral psychologist Karl Lashley

Make a small change in your daily life for 21 consecutive days. You may start to form the habit and gradually develop a more eco-friendly lifestyle.

Let’s join the “21-Day Sustainable Diet” challenge. At least one healthy meal a day, which is plant-based and has less meat consumption, to reduce your carbon footprint.

How to participate:
1. Post a photo of your sustainable diet on Instagram / Facebook (either in your Story or as a Post) every day.
2. Tag a friend and invite them to accept the challenge.
3. Use the hashtag #tivoli21dayschallenge

Awards:
For students of Tivoli: Those who successfully complete the 21-day challenge will be awarded with a certificate at the Graduation Ceremony cum Learning Experience Sharing this year.

For public: Those who successfully complete the 21-day challenge will be invited to attend our Graduation Ceremony cum Learning Experience Sharing this year, and will also be awarded with a certificate." role="button"></div><div><div data-hook="item-wrapper" class="gallery-item-wrapper visible cube-type-fit [object Object]" id="item-wrapper-be47fa4c-0fdb-4649-8c80-3e1166ab52e5_32" style="background-color:inherit;height:500px;width:500px;margin:0px"><div class="gallery-item-content item-content-regular image-item gallery-item-visible gallery-item gallery-item-preloaded grid-fit  " data-hook="image-item" style="width:500px;height:500px;margin-top:0;margin-left:0"><picture><img src="https://scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t39.30808-6/469321273_18022271573630559_130234376498004951_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=110&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=18de74&amp;efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=CJC9R1YLPX0Q7kNvwFCo28I&amp;_nc_oc=AdpMYaTNbomZO6e1k2nnVl_7P5i-PCMJF5VkdyHTBHlipKuzElHEokrdUqJVdOc0Vy4&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&amp;_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&amp;_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQHIIheloa9w0S-73rNuJiQdonZCW9zkAyeXCdopz2pZnzQEmogOhjiRwwgJYrOwrqgQMf4J6khx&amp;oh=00_Afz5E08wxGXhlynDYBY8HkTRIUzBK1-h2QxrxHVvQP6u2g&amp;oe=69CAE3DB" alt="🌏 「讓一個想法、或行動變成習慣，需要21天的時間。」—行為心理學家卡爾 雷須利(Karl Lashley)

