How do you know if your child is a hidden talent just waiting to be discovered? You don’t. But you can certainly try to find out by participating in the many extra curriculars primary schools have on offer! Thank you S.K.H. Tsing Yi Estate Ho Chak Wan Primary School for showing us all the different things we have to look forward to in P1 and how to Chinese Drum!" class="gallery-item-visible gallery-item gallery-item-preloaded" style="width:100%;height:100%" data-hook="gallery-item-image-img" loading="lazy"/></picture></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-hook="group-view" class="group-view group-view-34" style="--group-top:0px;--group-left:18700px;--group-width:550px;--group-right:auto" aria-hidden="false"><div data-id="0068dba4-73e7-4adf-8427-6cfb836d7f20_34" class="item-link-wrapper" data-idx="34" data-hook="item-link-wrapper" tabindex="-1"><div class="gallery-item-container item-container-regular has-custom-focus visible clickable" id="pgi0068dba473e74adf84276cfb836d7f20_34_34" data-hash="0068dba4-73e7-4adf-8427-6cfb836d7f20_34" data-id="0068dba4-73e7-4adf-8427-6cfb836d7f20_34" data-idx="34" data-hook="item-container" style="overflow-y:hidden;position:absolute;bottom:auto;margin:25px;top:0;left:18700px;right:auto;width:500px;height:500px;overflow:hidden;transition:opacity .2s ease;opacity:0;display:none"><div data-idx="34" id="item-action-0068dba4-73e7-4adf-8427-6cfb836d7f20_34" class="item-action" tabindex="-1" data-hook="item-action" aria-label="您知道每天只需閱讀 15 分鐘📖（任何語言）即可 
- 增長詞彙量和知識 
- 提供參與和建立與知識聯繫的機會 
