#喜氣洋洋幼小同樂慶新春🤩

Thanks for visiting and planning with us today, Principal Wong of TWGHs Wong Sze Sum Primary School! We’re so excited for the upcoming events we’ll be co-hosting together, including experiences to help make the primary transition smoother! 

Here’s a throwback to last year’s drone experience day and our lunar new year fair! 🤩" class="gallery-item-visible gallery-item gallery-item-preloaded" style="width:100%;height:100%" data-hook="gallery-item-image-img" loading="lazy"/></picture></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-hook="group-view" class="group-view group-view-46" style="--group-top:0px;--group-left:25300px;--group-width:550px;--group-right:auto" aria-hidden="false"><div data-id="9d3f5a20-335c-4004-a12a-86d56c1070a2_46" class="item-link-wrapper" data-idx="46" data-hook="item-link-wrapper" tabindex="-1"><div class="gallery-item-container item-container-regular has-custom-focus visible clickable" id="pgi9d3f5a20335c4004a12a86d56c1070a2_46_46" data-hash="9d3f5a20-335c-4004-a12a-86d56c1070a2_46" data-id="9d3f5a20-335c-4004-a12a-86d56c1070a2_46" data-idx="46" data-hook="item-container" style="overflow-y:hidden;position:absolute;bottom:auto;margin:25px;top:0;left:25300px;right:auto;width:500px;height:500px;overflow:hidden;transition:opacity .2s ease;opacity:0;display:none"><div data-idx="46" id="item-action-9d3f5a20-335c-4004-a12a-86d56c1070a2_46" class="item-action" tabindex="-1" data-hook="item-action" aria-label="開學第一天，很高興能結識新朋友及與同學相聚！！🏫 暑假過後，我們急不及待再次與朋友們一起分享、遊玩和玩堆砌遊戲！😄 快樂的時光讓小朋友樂而忘返，轉眼間放學了，與同學老師說再見真的有點難，期待明天的學習，再一起快樂地探索知識！💞

Finally our first day of school!!🏫 So excited to meet new friends and reunite with old ones after the break!😄 It’s been a while and we can’t wait to share, play and build together again!! Saying goodbye might still be a little tough, but it’ll get easier soon enough! 💞" role="button"></div><div><div data-hook="item-wrapper" class="gallery-item-wrapper visible cube-type-fit [object Object]" id="item-wrapper-9d3f5a20-335c-4004-a12a-86d56c1070a2_46" style="background-color:inherit;height:500px;width:500px;margin:0px"><div class="gallery-item-content item-content-regular image-item gallery-item-visible gallery-item gallery-item-preloaded grid-fit  video-item gallery-item-video" data-hook="image-item" style="width:500px;height:500px;margin-top:0;margin-left:0"><picture><img src="https://scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/499780061_1040643568028387_5116173355774269581_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=111&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=18de74&amp;efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0xJUFMuYmVzdF9pbWFnZV91cmxnZW4uQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=yFeeY8chrAMQ7kNvwHBEC5V&amp;_nc_oc=AdqWTWlSNfRbg8xuR0HE7Sp7eBRdmuiHOwoBkM3CZpmX32Lt_Cb8UOT9nTAMtrol_LA&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&amp;_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&amp;_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQGAIwddeSzo11r8t1M6p3zk9SSlyc5UCDJ5cCD8BBkeVsAVNMDnBCak-3mjYGv_pzIkC9-pzcOi&amp;oh=00_Afw2lxqNtlB-uKduK75SG7J95XNtih_Yu0JBuDU8KsnaXQ&amp;oe=69CAB03D" alt="開學第一天，很高興能結識新朋友及與同學相聚！！🏫 暑假過後，我們急不及待再次與朋友們一起分享、遊玩和玩堆砌遊戲！😄 快樂的時光讓小朋友樂而忘返，轉眼間放學了，與同學老師說再見真的有點難，期待明天的學習，再一起快樂地探索知識！💞

