<!-- warmup data start -->
<script type="application/json" id="wix-warmup-data">{"platform":{"ssrPropsUpdates":[{"comp-m7ioopvl_r_comp-m010jxj2":{"collapsed":true},"comp-m7ioopvl_r_comp-lp9pu1jk":{"deleted":false,"manualStyleParams":{"behaviourParams_item_clickAction":"EXPAND","layoutParams_structure_galleryLayout":2,"layoutParams_structure_numberOfColumns":3,"layoutParams_structure_scrollDirection":"HORIZONTAL","layoutParams_structure_itemSpacing":50,"layoutParams_crop_ratios":1,"layoutParams_navigationArrows_size":50,"layoutParams_navigationArrows_padding":32,"layoutParams_navigationArrows_container_type":"BOX","layoutParams_structure_numberOfGridRows":1},"wixSDKItems":[{"type":"video","description":"「喜氣洋洋幼小同樂迎新春」在一片歡樂、熱鬧的氣氛中圓滿結束！🧧✨\n感謝各位家長和小朋友的熱情參與，讓今年的活動笑聲不斷、溫馨滿載！🎊\n\n🦁 K3・宏福醒獅隊\n氣勢十足的醒獅隊霸氣登場，展現滿滿團隊精神！K3小朋友的精彩演出，值得大家熱烈掌聲！👏\n\n🎨 K2・親子獅頭創作\n創意無限、手工細緻，每個獅頭都獨一無二，盡顯親子合作的力量與美感！🧡\n\n🌸 PN・K1 迎春接福載歌載舞\n小小年紀，台風穩健，可愛度爆燈，為全場添上最燦爛的新年氣氛！🧧🧨\n\n🎯 攤位遊戲・人人樂\n大人細路齊齊投入，玩得盡興，笑聲洋溢全場！\n\n🐎 預祝大家馬年進步、龍馬精神！\n一齊以滿滿活力，迎接喜氣洋洋的馬年！🧨❤️\n\n🐴 The Joyful Chinese New Year Fair has come to a wonderful end! 🧧✨\nA huge thank you to every parent and child for your enthusiasm and energy—you made this year’s celebration truly special! 🎊\n\n🦁 K3 – Tivoli Lion Dance Team\nOur spirited little lions took the stage with confidence and teamwork. Let’s give a big round of applause for our K3 performers! 👏\n\n🎨 K2 – Parent-Child Lion Head Craft\nCreativity shone through every unique lion head. Such exquisite craftsmanship—truly a masterpiece of parent-child collaboration! 🧡\n\n🌸 PN & K1 – Spring Welcoming Performance\nSo young, yet so poised! Their adorable performance filled the hall with joy and New Year spirit. 🧧🧨\n\n🎯 Game Booths – Fun for All\nParents and kids dove into the fun together—endless laughter and happy memories!\n\n🐎 Wishing you all progress in the Year of the Horse,\nwith vitality, joy, and a vibrant start to the New Year! 🧨❤️","alt":"「喜氣洋洋幼小同樂迎新春」在一片歡樂、熱鬧的氣氛中圓滿結束！🧧✨\n感謝各位家長和小朋友的熱情參與，讓今年的活動笑聲不斷、溫馨滿載！🎊\n\n🦁 K3・宏福醒獅隊\n氣勢十足的醒獅隊霸氣登場，展現滿滿團隊精神！K3小朋友的精彩演出，值得大家熱烈掌聲！👏\n\n🎨 K2・親子獅頭創作\n創意無限、手工細緻，每個獅頭都獨一無二，盡顯親子合作的力量與美感！🧡\n\n🌸 PN・K1 迎春接福載歌載舞\n小小年紀，台風穩健，可愛度爆燈，為全場添上最燦爛的新年氣氛！🧧🧨\n\n🎯 攤位遊戲・人人樂\n大人細路齊齊投入，玩得盡興，笑聲洋溢全場！\n\n🐎 預祝大家馬年進步、龍馬精神！\n一齊以滿滿活力，迎接喜氣洋洋的馬年！🧨❤️\n\n🐴 The Joyful Chinese New Year Fair has come to a wonderful end! 🧧✨\nA huge thank you to every parent and child for your enthusiasm and energy—you made this year’s celebration truly special! 🎊\n\n🦁 K3 – Tivoli Lion Dance Team\nOur spirited little lions took the stage with confidence and teamwork. Let’s give a big round of applause for our K3 performers! 👏\n\n🎨 K2 – Parent-Child Lion Head Craft\nCreativity shone through every unique lion head. Such exquisite craftsmanship—truly a masterpiece of parent-child collaboration! 🧡\n\n🌸 PN & K1 – Spring Welcoming Performance\nSo young, yet so poised! Their adorable performance filled the hall with joy and New Year spirit. 🧧🧨\n\n🎯 Game Booths – Fun for All\nParents and kids dove into the fun together—endless laughter and happy memories!\n\n🐎 Wishing you all progress in the Year of the Horse,\nwith vitality, joy, and a vibrant start to the New Year! 🧨❤️","src":"https:\/\/scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com\/o1\/v\/t2\/f2\/m86\/AQMiqM6teg-RrNvfSMNZZSR8Yp-DXDbBN4sTZZkRKQTydILt-1pF1srJ9UUw2sNm0fdVnTAG_SyTwc8HX2piGoo4t3K2VDzxNDW8S1E.mp4?_nc_cat=106&_nc_sid=5e9851&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=1WQMxy_UAJMQ7kNvwGkCSUv&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6MTgwNzIyNDkzMjY2MzA1NTksImFzc2V0X2FnZV9kYXlzIjo0MSwidmlfdXNlY2FzZV9pZCI6MTA4MjcsImR1cmF0aW9uX3MiOjQ1LCJ1cmxnZW5fc291cmNlIjoid3d3In0%3D&ccb=17-1&vs=42469c6179b7edc5&_nc_-2r-WrqeaQBUCKAJDMywXQEbIcrAgxJwYEmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MREAdf4HZZapAQA&_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&_nc_zt=28&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQEGR767Gx3G9OVfpE9CnJ1Ncvc36xF-suCsGou2VJHkHzQ_u7g1wKa6AH9jmX7xTnTQLhqkqEBt&oh=00_Afy56I3D4osNdDbQNR3pXv7Zc0DJ8M9s8nS-pJ1g3BRLBA&oe=69C6DC57","thumbnail