術代表隊成員，香港十大傑青🇭🇰、世界太極拳錦標賽兩項金牌得主🥇、世界運動會巡迥賽（香港站）銅牌得主🥉\n\nToday, a star martial arts guest visited our school!🤩\n\nShe is Juanita Mok, an alumna from our very first PN class, now a member of Hong Kong’s Martial Arts Team, one of Hong Kong’s Ten Outstanding Young Persons🇭🇰, a double gold medalist at the World Taijiquan Championships🥇, and a bronze medalist at The World Games Tour (Hong Kong)🥉.","src":"https:\/\/scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t51.75761-15\/496240441_18040043201630559_1521084854656152154_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=111&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=yFrmBbmqUFgQ7kNvwHqVMOa&_nc_oc=Adp_2XMBPePZRJODIBHqEOAMR60gT5ihCNNGh8pGqWYNdkiCoQ3RlQmpjUnsIGRFv7s&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQGDCdw_ugRBGNTtoU_0oFOwn4_1tnSLUJXH7m1DJPL0OLkJxCRsRMHw6M9H-HO2XgtUYvGRR1zS&oh=00_AfzROpv_axeYHUP8SVVdf8S51b59VnssA80AarfW0lLPQA&oe=69CADB9B","link":"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/p\/DJZD546PJMc\/","timestamp":"2025-05-08T11:52:22.000Z","children":[{"type":"image","src":"https:\/\/scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t51.75761-15\/496240441_18040043201630559_1521084854656152154_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=111&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=yFrmBbmqUFgQ7kNvwHqVMOa&_nc_oc=Adp_2XMBPePZRJODIBHqEOAMR60gT5ihCNNGh8pGqWYNdkiCoQ3RlQmpjUnsIGRFv7s&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQHO3VIRz2auEqJlqHZBQibo6y9T47bTlHocc-XzZjTHZ56om_jSDEdgcV9XEYeyHBblWQi9dRUm&oh=00_AfzCy091GxffEzaxoFuUvgoR_bvWQsLBWPaU7Ge9qYsRig&oe=69CADB9B"},{"type":"image","src":"https:\/\/scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t51.75761-15\/496515909_18040043192630559_9088605848448345820_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=110&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=yx