5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=ueOwBr-AfDkQ7kNvwFNI2v2&_nc_oc=AdqIfLFLnaTPIABuyOYuivpupxz0cSA_fVUJ_7yIu_-jrZ-KpzVHW3dX77OqckCKxuY&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQE98U9CF1ribvlThfCWv0dDNT_JKb0TtI2BNAv0oWYaaknQzxtMfTJ0SDOwFih9eevf-pqpQGna&oh=00_Afz9_LnM8Sq39Gbt8lvC6rCu7_gmOKVVgSIoZiwrw2zEKg&oe=69CAAFA7"},{"type":"image","src":"https:\/\/scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t51.75761-15\/485584949_18034997429630559_8886889106898825194_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=103&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=4ZWiq6oAxasQ7kNvwGu9s8O&_nc_oc=Adq5nA2xPzfNsTiqRL5ZqMWLWrUgrCGN_ERx2cxKEREbi5qNnf-rs0p5q8Zt7q7lk8c&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQHir4SaaNT2AjB9tUG6mmYBj56MMbsNRH7-xCanCNJhu50qZJcnI1g3-ksy3iuZp_xH3U6nJkUs&oh=00_AfxFXZSugw7KDX47SB_io912_FzK7C-FaicbBVAE5SuTHQ&oe=69CAB155"}],"width":218,"height":218},{"type":"carousel","description":"兒童安全及健康一直是我們最關注的重點工作。為兒童身心健康，就要大家一齊做好防疫工作！🤝🏼\n\n農曆年假後的首個工作日，學校特意邀請香港紅十字會的專業團隊為全體員工進行防疫講座、實地視察，進一步加強團隊的防疫能力！💪🏼\n\n下一步就係要召募學生及家長義工擔任「健康大使」。祝大家蛇年進步、平安大吉、身體健康！❤🌷🙏🏼\n\nChildren’s safety and health have always been our top priority. To ensure the physical and mental well-being of children, we must all work together on preventive measures! 🤝🏼\n\nOn the first working day after the Lunar New Year break, the school specially invited a professional team from the Hong Kong Red Cross to conduct a seminar and on-site inspection for all staff, further strengthening the team‘s preventive strategies! 💪🏼\n\nThe next step is to recruit student and parent volunteers to act as ”Health Ambassadors.“ Wishing everyone progress, safety, and good health in the Year of the Snake! ❤🌷🙏🏼","alt":"兒童安全及健康一直是我們最關注的重點工作。為兒童身心健康，就要大家一齊做好防疫工作！🤝🏼\n\n農曆年假後的首個工作日，學校特意邀請香港紅十字會的專業團隊為全體員工進行防疫講座、實地視察，進一步加強團隊的防疫能力！💪🏼\n\n下一步就係要召募學生及家長義工擔任「健康大使」。祝大家蛇年進步、平安大吉、身體健康！❤🌷🙏🏼\n\nChildren’s safety and health have always been our top priority. To ensure the physical and mental well-being of children, we must all work together on preventive measures! 🤝🏼\n\nOn the first working day after the Lunar New Year break, the school specially invited a professional team from the Hong Kong Red Cross to conduct a seminar and on-site inspection for all staff, further strengthening the team‘s preventive strategies! 💪🏼\n\nThe next step is to recruit student and parent volunteers to act as ”Health Ambassadors.“ Wishing everyone progress, safety, and good health in the Year of the Snake! ❤🌷🙏🏼","src":"https:\/\/scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t51.75761-15\/476401515_18029733770630559_1862883722225435149_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=108&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=bKPKRH-_0tkQ7kNvwHaiuce&_nc_oc=AdryG-c8LNoXn5iCVN6wh5fhc8IBujESZ64LG_O0Datj9akEMWBG8kUIbJJeVk-ElU0&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQGAF8MnVN7asua4DO5o6eAPOwuo6RO5kI9ebGoH9sB-aYJShZvKRb-LN2XPjUht1LcobGd9sK6d&oh=00_AfzHb8LgMIVpfJpAYTMo6qvMifkeNYPdsXZ5sTyxmvuHlw&oe=69CACE0D","link":"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/p\/DFuMojAPjdi\/","timestamp":"2025-02-06T06:47:07.000Z","children":[{"type":"image","src":"https:\/\/scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t51.75761-15\/476401515_18029733770630559_1862883722225435149_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=108&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=bKPKRH-_0tkQ7kNvwHaiuce&_nc_oc=AdryG-c8LNoXn5iCVN6wh5fhc8IBujESZ64LG_O0Datj9akEMWBG8kUIbJJeVk-ElU0&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQGHdbtzyRrr73F9bZsALXOwLaTMsqBzC-zj2vBwf8zsQBUCpZWxuf93b-pzPjJ8HRe2sj7DnuHC&oh=00_Afylc2nlI9-BURzvp4jD3a_rBhA5uIsiFYxA9c5u8-m2dg&o