Merry Christmas🎄 and a Happy New Year🎆\n\nOur children from Tivoli Anglo-Chinese Kindergarten and Tivoli Nursery(Ching Fu) Tivoli Kindergarten(Ching Fu) took part in the Christmas Carol Marathon 2024 at the start of December. On Winter Solstice, we hosted \n‘Love & Care Christmas Show 2024’ at the Tsing Yi Athletic Association Sports Ground to celebrate the holiday together!","alt":"祝大家聖誕🎄及新年快樂🎆\n\n宏福中英文幼稚園及宏福幼兒園(青富)宏福幼稚園(青富)的小朋友12月初已經率先參與青衣城歌舞馬拉松表演活動，冬至當日更假青衣體育會球場舉辦「愛心送暖迎聖誕」與社區一起歡渡聖誕！\n\nIt’s the perfect moment to extend warm wishes for a Merry Christmas🎄 and a Happy New Year🎆\n\nOur children from Tivoli Anglo-Chinese Kindergarten and Tivoli Nursery(Ching Fu) Tivoli Kindergarten(Ching Fu) took part in the Christmas Carol Marathon 2024 at the start of December. On Winter Solstice, we hosted \n‘Love & Care Christmas Show 2024’ at the Tsing Yi Athletic Association Sports Ground to celebrate the holiday together!","src":"https:\/\/scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t51.75761-15\/471675615_18024669206630559_390657544391343103_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=108&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=BMSV14He1LoQ7kNvwFKfcA1&_nc_oc=AdoKkGXwLWmMyogCYenf1ipW3WA5vUFZiATO2g1NOHCuuJl8ahNjooBUdg36UkHaf7s&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQGEVjBxHvabhfUM6zFw4vLBcUgMuSdomEM5Z2ZS31q9mZBdTTOV5eKvwaRfAzrwUXDNV4xDBOS_&oh=00_AfyQ5OlagRJW-dwbp1j7SpP9iA9KJP4SuEINum1cqR-62A&oe=69CAB852","link":"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/p\/DEBhCoev0D-\/","timestamp":"2024-12-26T01:48:14.000Z","children":[{"type":"image","src":"https:\/\/scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t51.75761-15\/471675615_18024669206630559_390657544391343103_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=108&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=BMSV14He1LoQ7kNvwFKfcA1&_nc_oc=AdoKkGXwLWmMyogCYenf1ipW3WA5vUFZiATO2g1NOHCuuJl8ahNjooBUdg36UkHa