&_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQFmXpKjVTizMfGda9ds3L98YNmJ6vfvd-RoRyKhyoKIJjx24LEKwrAV9dOjBu6A4qVJOT05dskY&oh=00_AfxRwibExKA5dpxGNuiCE1nxRxqcxhzD-J8B9if00HTaLA&oe=69CABA22"},{"type":"image","src":"https:\/\/scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t39.30808-6\/459410851_18011083598630559_9164779654856070812_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=102&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=sYVcxO-MLpsQ7kNvwFUmqgz&_nc_oc=AdrJt71MJ32VGXET26ECSFlaNtotRvqRHCUNEKEbIXh0kpZWlxRaXLM8fMon_XXitS8&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQEL1gVcvKwGwoq8E7gzfbpeZjlCtXFMD4KOGmesHrPXbpZOT5kzGNhbMq2bgxbZ0Sfr4TQASsya&oh=00_AfzQZfbCfDVuWXnBzMMY2yC8aFVySd9NZKETjY3FC09QRg&oe=69CAD2F4"}],"width":218,"height":218},{"type":"carousel","description":"放完暑假，嚟到探校日喇！\n今日好開心見到各位家長同小朋友出席👧🏻👦🏻，一齊同老師見面👩🏻‍🏫，參觀一下學校同課室🏫\n我哋星期一返學見！🎒\n\nNow that summer break is over, it’s time for the family school visit day! \nIt’s thrilling to see all the parents and kids here today 👧🏻👦🏻, connecting with the teachers 👩🏻‍🏫 and exploring the school and classrooms 🏫. \nLooking forward to seeing everyone back at school on Monday! 🎒","alt":"放完暑假，嚟到探校日喇！\n今日好開心見到各位家長同小朋友出席👧🏻👦🏻，一齊同老師見面👩🏻‍🏫，參觀一下學校同課室🏫\n我哋星期一返學見！🎒\n\nNow that summer break is over, it’s time for the family school visit day! \nIt’s thrilling to see all the parents and kids here today 👧🏻👦🏻, connecting with the teachers 👩🏻‍🏫 and exploring the school and classrooms 🏫. \nLooking forward to seeing everyone back at school on Monday! 🎒","src":"https:\/\/scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t39.30808-6\/469596652_18022275638630559_7337658554544794294_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=111&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=5bWao9bhPGEQ7kNvwGIGfO-&_nc_oc=Adqvy-pS2uYsExLQUALq55vhZlKRdo15MNS0-sW7C-Jxi9Ynxru2cclv10AzBLiddGo&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&edm=AN