&_nc_ohc=vUyHGMgRo7YQ7kNvwHZ9SxS&_nc_oc=AdpLSkHmadgrmjCSkkDfqnQl4VgsUENtcZC6HtsnCWCeOUhrJA-Scm8ocBFxfR5jH5k&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQFs51MSrGnfeMPwIxne_Tw_m-GMXJUBiJTU2nhN6jbOmk0XqcAPnp-MJU_6PyBmMH-tbXQW6B7A&oh=00_Afy7n9KmcNlCrL440hWkrS7W6qCI-cxTlccjMuRKebBxuw&oe=69CAD114"}],"width":218,"height":218},{"type":"image","description":"📣宏福幼稚園(青富)宏福幼兒園(青富)嘅開放日就喺2024年8月24號喇📣\n\n當日有幾場限定活動，包括：\n🎨七感探索之旅\n💃🏻創意綜合式幼兒肢體音樂體驗活動\n📚英語\/普通話\/廣東話故事劇場\n\n每個活動都設有名額，唔想錯過嘅就快啲嚟報名喇！\n\n🔗登記參加開放日限定活動：\nhttps:\/\/forms.gle\/e9erN31CvVa6jVv76\n\n📣Tivoli Kindergarten (Ching Fu) and Tivoli Nursery (Ching Fu) will be hosting open house on August 24, 2024📣\n\nThere will be several exclusive activities that day, including:\n🎨 Tivoli's Multisensory Exploration Journey\n💃🏻 Creative Integrated Early Childhood Music and Movement Experience \n📚 Tivoli's Storytime Theater\n\nSpots are limited for each activity, so sign up soon if you don't want to miss out!\n\n🔗Register to participate in the open house exclusive activities:\nhttps:\/\/forms.gle\/e9erN31CvVa6jVv76","alt":"📣宏福幼稚園(青富)宏福幼兒園(青富)嘅開放日就喺2024年8月24號喇📣\n\n當日有幾場限定活動，包括：\n🎨七感探索之旅\n💃🏻創意綜合式幼兒肢體音樂體驗活動\n📚英語\/普通話\/廣東話故事劇場\n\n每個活動都設有名額，唔想錯過嘅就快啲嚟報名喇！\n\n🔗登記參加開放日限定活動：\nhttps:\/\/forms.gle\/e9erN31CvVa6jVv76\n\n📣Tivoli Kindergarten (Ching Fu) and Tivoli Nursery (Ching Fu) will be hosting open house on August 24, 2024📣\n\nThere will be several exclusive activities that day, including:\n🎨 Tivoli's Multisensory Exploration Journey\n💃🏻 Creative Integrated Early Childhood Music and Movement Experience \n📚 Tivoli's Storytime Theater\n\nSpots are limited for each activity, so sign up soon if you don't want to miss out!\n\n🔗Register to participate in the open house exclusive activities:\nhttps:\/\/forms.gle\/e9erN31CvVa6jVv76","src":"https:\/\/scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t51.82787-15\/624838566_18085197169933756_4842158696637132307_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=108&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiRkVFRC5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=JxwPtpJ5qxoQ7kNvwHGoOGO&_nc_oc=AdpGTJod6tWdLJbkffy94aNrEFbBut-s8UUw37THsN7np5ONViRDyqP6puq3JW9sLP8&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQF1pHY5_OfECxsddzSpdv33LsUGBnDv5zJWW2QVNuIyWX15mso693Cln9fNVaMYtDTb3mSr4Hly&oh=00_AfygXZJ0DAsVnEJFa1zahz617iwDl4lUGV4LJsJp06LFMw&oe=69CABF39","link":"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/p\/C-RU6KFy2oA\/","timestamp":"2024-08-05T02:01:42.000Z","width":218,"height":218},{"type":"carousel","description":"🌏 「讓一個想法、或行動變成習慣，需要21天的時間。」—行為心理學家卡爾 雷須利(Karl Lashley)\n\n連續21天，在日常生活中做一點微小改變。也許你會開始習慣，慢慢培養出對地球更好的生活方式。\n\n邀請你一起參加「永續飲食21天」挑戰，每日一餐多菜少肉，一起做到低碳排放。\n\n參加方法：\n1. 每天在Instagram \/ Facebook post一張你的永續飲食相片(Stoty或Post都可以)\n2. Tag一位朋友，邀請他\/她一同接受挑戰\n3. Hashtag #tivoli21dayschallenge \n\n獎項：\n本校學生：成功完成21天挑戰者，將於本年度成果分享會暨畢業典禮中頒發獎狀，以作鼓勵！\n公眾人士：成功完成21天挑戰者，將會邀請出席本年度成果分享會暨畢業典禮，並會頒發獎狀，以作鼓勵！\n\n🌏 It takes 21 days for an idea or action to become a habit.” - Behavioral psychologist Karl Lashley\n\nMake a small change in your daily life for 21 consecutive days. You may start to form the habit and gradually develop a more eco-friendly lifestyle.\n\nLet’s join the “21-Day Sustainable Diet” challenge. At least one healthy meal a day, which is plant-based and has less meat consumption, to reduce your carbon footprint.\n\nHow to participate:\n1. Post a photo of your sustainable diet on Instagram \/ Facebook (either in your Story or as a Post) every day.\n2. Tag a friend and invite them to accept the challenge.\n3. Use the hashtag #tivoli21dayschallenge\n\nAwards:\nFor students of Tivoli: Those who successfully complete the 21-day challenge will be awarded with a certificate at the Graduation Ceremony cum Learning Experience Sharing this year.\n\nFor public: Those who successfully complete the 21-day challenge will be invited to attend our Graduation Ceremony cum Learning Experience Sharing this year, and will also be awarded with a certificate.","alt":"🌏 「讓一個想法、或行動變成習慣，需要21天的時間。」—行為心理學家卡爾 雷須利(Karl Lashley)\n\n連續21天，在日常生活中做一點微小改變。也許你會開始習慣，慢慢培養出對地球更好的生活方式。\n\n邀請你一起參加「永續飲食21天」挑戰，每日一餐多菜少肉，一起做到低碳排放。\n\n參加方法：\n1. 每天在Instagram \/ Facebook post一張你的永續飲食相片(Stoty或Post都可以)\n2. Tag一位朋友，邀請他\/她一同接受挑戰\n3. Hashtag #tivoli21dayschallenge \n\n獎項：\n本校學生：成功完成21天挑戰者，將於本年度成果分享會暨畢業典禮中頒發獎狀，以作鼓勵！\n公眾人士：成功完成21天挑戰者，將會邀請出席本年度成果分享會暨畢業典禮，並會頒發獎狀，以作鼓勵！\n\n🌏 It takes 21 days for an idea or action to become a habit.” - Behavioral psychologist Karl Lashley\n\nMake a small change in your daily life for 21 consecutive days. You may start to form the habit and gradually develop a more eco-friendly lifestyle.\n\nLet’s join the “21-Day Sustainable Diet” challenge. At least one healthy meal a day, which is plant-based and has less meat consumption, to reduce your carbon footprint.\n\nHow to participate:\n1. Post a photo of your sustainable diet on Instagram \/ Facebook (either in your Story or as a Post) every day.\n2. Tag a friend and invite them to accept the challenge.\n3. Use the hashtag #tivoli21dayschallenge\n\nAwards:\nFor students of Tivoli: Those who successfully complete the 21-day challenge will be awarded with a certificate at the Graduation Ceremony cum Learning Experience Sharing this year.\n\nFor public: Those who successfully complete the 21-day challenge will be invited to attend our Graduation Ceremony cum Learning Experience Sharing this year, and will also be awarded with a certificate.","src":"https:\/\/scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t39.30808-6\/469321273_18022271573630559_130234376498004951_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=110&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=CJC9R1YLPX0Q7kNvwFCo28I&_nc_oc=AdpMYaTNbomZO6e1k2nnVl_7P5i-PCMJF5VkdyHTBHlipKuzElHEokrdUqJVdOc0Vy4&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQHIIheloa9w0S-73rNuJiQdonZCW9zkAyeXCdopz2pZnzQEmogOhjiRwwg