UI97OxSOjlEPgkCq0o4EMasLPaeU7BgjPqFMCG4g&oe=69CAD1E8"}],"width":218,"height":218},{"type":"carousel","description":"透過參加不同的體驗活動，可以讓我們發掘到小朋友的隱藏天賦﹗感謝聖公會青衣邨何澤芸小學提供機會，讓K2及K3的小朋友進行體驗中國鼓樂活動。\n\n升小銜接活動系列持續進行中，期待下次到其他小學進行各種不同的體驗。\n\nHow do you know if your child is a hidden talent just waiting to be discovered? You don’t. But you can certainly try to find out by participating in the many extra curriculars primary schools have on offer! Thank you S.K.H. Tsing Yi Estate Ho Chak Wan Primary School for showing us all the different things we have to look forward to in P1 and how to Chinese Drum!","alt":"透過參加不同的體驗活動，可以讓我們發掘到小朋友的隱藏天賦﹗感謝聖公會青衣邨何澤芸小學提供機會，讓K2及K3的小朋友進行體驗中國鼓樂活動。\n\n升小銜接活動系列持續進行中，期待下次到其他小學進行各種不同的體驗。\n\nHow do you know if your child is a hidden talent just waiting to be discovered? You don’t. But you can certainly try to find out by participating in the many extra curriculars primary schools have on offer! Thank you S.K.H. Tsing Yi Estate Ho Chak Wan Primary School for showing us all the different things we have to look forward to in P1 and how to Chinese Drum!","src":"https:\/\/scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t51.71878-15\/625020796_4227410054243297_6404292301004230042_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=111&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=KN6EwrsQ210Q7kNvwEw6CX0&_nc_oc=AdozTV7hAxxpn85K9jUX1rJPCZ-TliduvNeskO8vUBosBL3NAkOLoqVhw8uikeB84cs&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQG9jSO-pLO8gc0sXzXdlIbXlcDUqvDnZEuCJZGxkXuTXDj-a_oxgy_KAAhgtm_YG3kePQhUNJPD&oh=00_AfzoO8fqVhVFKaFUwlcsD4zUckUQ_SF7YDC2cKLfrGux3g&oe=69CADE62","link":"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/p\/C6gEXJFP0Hl\/","timestamp":"2024-05-03T09:20:08.000Z","children":[{"type":"video","src":"https:\/\/scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com\/o1\/v\/t16\/f2\/m69\/AQOc7D1mzoBECmHXM50PWtVlmZI56vYCoRwC1FKSVTJ8-uLt_f-J16wyTZjAtQ5duXIkp3EYKS_CHQGUtlJu4L9V.mp4?strext=1&_nc_cat=102&_nc_sid=5e9851