ub29fMdm_mrew&oe=69CAD5C2"}],"width":218,"height":218},{"type":"carousel","description":"到社區一齊享受節日歡樂氣氛實在是賞心樂事！非常感謝停低欣賞各班幼兒表演的觀眾及宏福團隊的完美配合，令每一位幼兒都自信地站在舞台上進行賞心悅目的表演！感謝所有參與的家庭和嘉賓，並祝聖誕及新年快樂！🎄⭐️🎄\nWhat a beautiful day to step outside and spread the holiday cheer! Applause for all our students for having the courage to step onto the stage and thank you to everyone who stopped by, but most of all, a HUGE thank you to our amazing team of staff for making this all happen!! From our family to yours - MERRY CHRISTMAS AND A HAPPY NEW YEAR! 🎅🏻🔔🎅🏻","alt":"到社區一齊享受節日歡樂氣氛實在是賞心樂事！非常感謝停低欣賞各班幼兒表演的觀眾及宏福團隊的完美配合，令每一位幼兒都自信地站在舞台上進行賞心悅目的表演！感謝所有參與的家庭和嘉賓，並祝聖誕及新年快樂！🎄⭐️🎄\nWhat a beautiful day to step outside and spread the holiday cheer! Applause for all our students for having the courage to step onto the stage and thank you to everyone who stopped by, but most of all, a HUGE thank you to our amazing team of staff for making this all happen!! From our family to yours - MERRY CHRISTMAS AND A HAPPY NEW YEAR! 🎅🏻🔔🎅🏻","src":"https:\/\/scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t39.30808-6\/469452007_18022255211630559_3893308607667635701_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=108&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=-nHmbaTB1RAQ7kNvwEBZVJ1&_nc_oc=AdrF4wGUzVTwaYYrPHKJEDD8jORghqzWS7ey-lb2SHKPO0hNmMnzRlhw2nejonl4FWM&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQHYgqK_9AG9oF0jAePZLX4nVadi8Q4e0fcwo6DWOIch2lhxqkE2To8ernvKp2vnRxz84_Mzaaey&oh=00_AfyeZ4c1wMqYva7eI9WAPUR4VH8CLdCqmsOlcX7xQ0CWWg&oe=69CAD394","link":"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/p\/C0-cG1sPFId\/","timestamp":"2023-12-18T01:16:29.000Z","children":[{"type":"image","src":"https:\/\/scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t39.30808-6\/469452007_18022255211630559_3893308607667635701_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=108&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=-nHmbaTB1RAQ7kNvwEBZ