」的活動並不容易…但一大班人進行就安全啦！🤣\n\n從嘗試各種形式的南瓜到在黑暗中發現蝙蝠，這一天也充滿了感官刺激的活動！看看這些冒險者走了! 🤩\n\nIt’s not easy approaching different staff members for a bit of trick or treating…but there’s always safety in numbers 🤣 From trying pumpkin in its various forms to spotting bats in the dark, the day is also packed with activities to stimulate all our senses! Look at these risk-takers go! 🤩","alt":"有些幼兒覺得「不給糖就搗蛋」的活動並不容易…但一大班人進行就安全啦！🤣\n\n從嘗試各種形式的南瓜到在黑暗中發現蝙蝠，這一天也充滿了感官刺激的活動！看看這些冒險者走了! 🤩\n\nIt’s not easy approaching different staff members for a bit of trick or treating…but there’s always safety in numbers 🤣 From trying pumpkin in its various forms to spotting bats in the dark, the day is also packed with activities to stimulate all our senses! Look at these risk-takers go! 🤩","src":"https:\/\/scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t39.30808-6\/398213769_17971239059630559_5099667210203949444_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=111&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=kLL5xPgrz_kQ7kNvwF8Byi_&_nc_oc=AdqIBdGk5prgyZw871KFqu9Hd2WQjscPr87Dso2pj6PeA5hrmvzO9btqtoFQj03Je3U&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQHLksbPfmRnwAd3KkfOYM8vwsA5_zRh_Topl04g4Uljd1U7UxeRJG4dl4w1K3qXZXQVkSJclnuS&oh=00_AfyRhfVy8piUUggUcECyX6t2zhxoXUp2qkPAvDMmW8AafQ&oe=69CAB78D","link":"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/p\/CzIoQrTvaNX\/","timestamp":"2023-11-02T07:12:18.000Z","children":[{"type":"image","src":"https:\/\/scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t39.30808-6\/398213769_17971239059630559_5099667210203949444_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=111&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=kLL5xPgrz_kQ7kNvwF8Byi_&_nc_oc=AdqIBdGk5prgyZw871KFqu9Hd2WQjscPr87Dso2pj6PeA5hrmvzO9btqtoFQj03Je3U&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQEouQtBOLxZroMr4CIai_l1CmQd4Dm11TvKa3tLuIDMSLKbRoi1h