4_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=111&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=PJBrtMhrmk4Q7kNvwHVtuwQ&_nc_oc=AdoUu22R3vZRMHJpQ5ADygtVs0d06egR9L3wa0TjN1HNOakGMWMzb2004t_oFms-Uac&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQH0C0U0WEaigt8pvnDmcTn9DB_HpxL-DEnjYYIbajgomL-lzAobSR1KcOOgLI9DEbPIVbLzd71y&oh=00_Afz71HbvEt_vhs1LOBdnvlGg5go--pSWlBDF8UNPsclKyQ&oe=69CADB3F"},{"type":"image","src":"https:\/\/scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com\/v\/t39.30808-6\/377500359_17964169100630559_2702151485625408678_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=104&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=LxAbObZufzgQ7kNvwFNgP5S&_nc_oc=Adqn0gMgJ5r-r5qX6TqNiFD-MW2Xm5imZnZ_KtxaNMJRvsN4c5AJ-Ovq7DzmcKyLoEQ&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-den2-1.cdninstagram.com&edm=ANo9K5cEAAAA&_nc_gid=xYx4SqPQHPDzSWtIVROrqw&_nc_tpa=Q5bMBQH1Wz7U4geT2O5466TvZIsCQQeWU01qPYeXYOqGVlJt9xQzOSsvq5HWuLOdM-kyohNouuBC--rn&oh=00_AfwVu98Fk1cxJSeGVJXQAqUrgbSxfMd-kJy90vpDgfW1HQ&oe=69CAE59F"}],"width":218,"height":218},{"type":"video","description":"開學第一天，很高興能結識新朋友及與同學相聚！！🏫 暑假過後，我們急不及待再次與朋友們一起分享、遊玩和玩堆砌遊戲！😄 快樂的時光讓小朋友樂而忘返，轉眼間放學了，與同學老師說再見真的有點難，期待明天的學習，再一起快樂地探索知識！💞\n\nFinally our first day of school!!🏫 So excited to meet new friends and reunite with old ones after the break!😄 It’s been a while and we can’t wait to share, play and build together again!! Saying goodbye might still be a little tough, but it’ll get easier soon enough! 💞","alt":"開學第一天，很高興能結識新朋友及與同學相聚！！🏫 暑假過後，我們急不及待再次與朋友們一起分享、遊玩和玩堆砌遊戲！😄 快樂的時光讓小朋友樂而忘返，轉眼間放學了，與同學老師說再見真的有點難，期待明天的學習，再一起快樂地探索知識！💞\n\nFinally our first day of school!!🏫 So excited to meet new friends and reunite with old ones after the break!😄 It’s been a while and we can’t wait to share, play and build together again!! Saying goodbye might still be a little tough, but it’ll get easier soon enough! 💞","src":"https:\/\/scontent-den2-1.cdninstagra